This new motor technology conceived by Canon
for this lens, and for the new 18-135 lens,

00:00:57.330 --> 00:01:04.160
allows precise, smooth, fluid motored movement control,
for photography as well as video

00:01:04.360 --> 00:01:08.019
So let's try and have fun in the streets of
Paris with this new lens

00:01:09.279 --> 00:01:13.030
So the video recording autofocus does not
work with the 5D Mark III we are using today,

00:01:13.030 --> 00:01:16.430
