Yes, the autofocus focuses very quickly

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:07.900
It focuses a little bit faster than the 50mm 1,2 lens

00:02:07.900 --> 00:02:11.100
The motor is also very, very quiet

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:16.200
In this urban scenery, I was not able to hear anything at all

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:20.500
It is a real pleasure to use it

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:24.600
Very smooth

00:02:26.700 --> 00:02:31.600
In terms of autofocus, I think this is the best among all of my lenses

