00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:53.300
My success rate on this series is quite high

00:03:55.500 --> 00:03:59.400
I would not go as far as sayong this is a sport lens,

00:03:59.700 --> 00:04:03.900
But for everyday life and street photography, it's great

